{"lastModified":1775130925231,"uri":"c::21222387982::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (US/BVI), Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards\n\nMeet Elysian, a newly upgraded BALI 5.4 that sets the standard for luxury catamaran charters in the BVIs. Every detail has been carefully crafted to deliver an extraordinary experience, from expansive lounge areas and spacious cabins to an impressive collection of premium water toys.\n\n– BEST IN CLASS –\nStep aboard one of the premier charter catamarans in the BVIs and discover why Elysian stands apart. You'll be captivated by her expansive bedrooms, premium amenities, and thoughtful design that maximizes both comfort and adventure.\n\n– 2025 UPGRADES –\nElysian receives continuous investment to ensure she feels brand new every season. This year's enhancements include luxurious SeaDek flooring throughout for supreme comfort, plush new exterior and interior cushions perfect for soaking up the Caribbean sun, and premium linens and bedding that guarantee restful nights.\n\nOn the water, experience the thrill of Elysian's powerful new 40hp Gala dinghy with upgraded engine. With an extensive selection of water toys, including an E-Foil, adventure awaits at every anchorage.\n\n– EXPERT CREW –\nCaptain Liam and Chef Kelsey are seasoned professionals dedicated to delivering exceptional charter experiences. Their attention to detail and commitment to first-class service ensures your every need is anticipated and met, creating those special moments that make you feel like royalty throughout your week aboard.\n\nDon't settle for ordinary when you can create memories that will last a lifetime. On Elysian, every detail comes together to craft the perfect Caribbean escape.","blueprint":{"name":"ELYSIAN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6039e1f0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6052c120-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::603a7e30-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::605447c1-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::605495e0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::604e2d40-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6051fdd0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::603b1a70-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60379800-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60533650-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::605447c0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6052c121-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60509e40-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60566aa0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::603b4180-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6053d290-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60524bf0-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::60535d60-b10e-11f0-b39d-93c2a8a3ef4a/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Bali Catamarans","model":"Bali 5.4","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::a0201b56-b3ee-11ed-8a74-325096b39f47","name":"Tortola","coordinates":{"latitude":18.4335216,"longitude":-64.63325746},"country":"British Virgin Islands"},"cruisingCapacity":0,"builtYear":2021,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"","refitYear":2025,"topSpeed":10,"cruiseSpeed":8,"fuelCapacity":"","cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"Queen Cabins","value":"3"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":5,"length":16.77,"beam":8.84,"draft":1.25,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"","amenities":[{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Special Diets"},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Sailing Instruction"},{"label":"Gym/Exercise Equipment"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Children Allowed"},{"label":"Bar"},{"label":"Coffee / espresso machine"}],"toys":[{"label":"eFoil (Fliteboard Air)"},{"label":"Sea scooters","quantity":"4"},{"label":"Paddle boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Subwing"},{"label":"Wakeboard"},{"label":"Towable tube"},{"label":"10' floating dock"},{"label":"Snorkel gear"},{"label":"Beach games"},{"label":"Fishing gear"},{"label":"Pool noodles"},{"label":"Board games"},{"label":"Card games"},{"label":"Swim Platform"}],"entertainment":["Salon Stereo","Salon TV","Onboard WIFI"],"tenders":["14ft. dinghy with 40hp outboard"]},"crew":[{"name":"Liam Wilson","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3cd13480-b10d-11f0-8072-1db573fbe574/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born and raised in Western Australia, Liam grew up racing dinghies with his dad before going on to work in surveying and mine engineering. Now a professional captain and ASA-certified sailing instructor, Liam brings a mix of calm confidence, teaching ability, and adventures spirit to every charter.\n\nWith years of experience captaining yachts across both the Caribbean and Mediterranean, Liam has an exceptional ability to read the room and create an itinerary built for each group matching their energy, from chilled out swims and sunset sails to action packed days of island hopping, snorkel safaris, and dinghy explorations.\n\nHe enjoys sharing his passion with guests, whether that means helping curious sailors get behind the helm, revealing hidden local gems, flying the drone at golden hour, or finding a quiet anchorage for a starlit dinner.\n\nWhen he’s not onboard, Liam is often off exploring new corners of the world, staying active with hikes or enjoying eFoil sessions. Occasionally jumping at the chance to join into a local regatta too!\n\nCERTIFICATES\n• RYA Yachtmaster Offshore (Commercially Endorsed)\n• RYA Ocean Theory\n• RYA Powerboat Level 2\n• ASA Sailing Instructor\n• Yachting Australia Instructor\n• STCW\n• PADI Advanced SCUBA Diver\n• UAV Licensed Drone Pilot\n• Advanced First Aid\n• AEC 1 & 2\n"},{"name":"Kelsey Wilson","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4eb0-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::54ed1480-b10d-11f0-8072-1db573fbe574/{imageVariant}","role":"Chef","bio":"Growing up in California, Kelsey was always drawn to the ocean, adventure, and bringing people together over great food. After a decade in the corporate world, she changed course to pursue her passion for hospitality—and hasn’t looked back. Now, as a yacht chef in the Caribbean, she combines her love of cooking and travel to create unforgettable experiences for guests to relax, connect, and enjoy.\n\nKelsey trained at Ashburton Chefs Academy in the UK, refining her skills in contemporary cuisine, and has since cooked aboard luxury charters in the Caribbean and Mediterranean. Her style is elevated yet approachable, focusing on vibrant, well-balanced flavors that showcase the best of international and island-inspired cuisine. Whether it's a beautifully plated dinner, a laid-back beach barbecue, or a colorful brunch spread, Kelsey takes pride in curating meals that feel special yet effortless.\n\nWhen she’s not in the galley, you’ll find her starting the day with a sunrise meditation, sipping coffee with a view, or uncovering hidden gems in each destination. She brings a warm, easygoing energy to life on board, allowing guests to feel right at home.\n\nShe's excited to create a dining experience that's just as incredible as the destinations you'll explore!\n\nCERTIFICATES\n• Certificate Culinary Arts - Ashburton Chefs Academy\n• Advanced Yacht Chef - Anchor & Apron\n• Culinary Arts Level 2 UK CTH\n• Level 2 Food Safety and Hygiene\n• RYA Day Skipper\n• STCW"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":3000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":3000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":3350000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":3350000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer/Winter - Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":3000000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":3000000,"amount":3000000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded"}],"total":3000000,"subTotal":3000000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"U.S. Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","U.S. Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.79221690684143,18.050874527948764],"bbox":[-65.0236328125,17.701708984375003,-64.58046875,18.385205078124997]},{"label":"British Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["N